  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"4 4 []\" style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp8e2\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd1qf8\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">作者 | 小小</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp1ym0\"><span style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd1nnb\"><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);font-size: 12px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">出品 | 网易科技</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp4rs\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd1dsz\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">重压之下，扎克伯格要“叛变”了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp1f3s\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdk3z\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">一年前，他还信誓旦旦地要把AI变成全人类的“免费午餐”，如今却突然决定把大门焊死。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppvk5\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048227\" data-ratio=\"0.7863636363636364\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;text-align: center;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"660\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4d207a42&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxUQyzLG8wxv3yibHKEOGpUogVianwrmRibw9tpg7pTqzqNHS3eicdDrRN2A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp246a\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdeva\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">在最近的内部调整中，昔日的开源明星Llama遭到冷落，取而代之的是一款代号为 “Avocado（牛油果）” 的神秘新模型，定档明年一季度。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp4vl\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048228\" data-ratio=\"1.353846153846154\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"585\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d9f90709&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxJYuSzGSuOr0jEyWqAY0JMWnCFLfmShNw3hKcMicyr3vsva9zczibHz3g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppppv\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd9rx\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">为了这张2026年才能兑现的船票，Meta不仅打破薪酬体系斥资143亿美元“天价挖人”，更在内部掀起了残酷的裁员风暴。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppto2\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd1qvx\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">然而，资本市场对此依然充满疑虑。面对战略的反复横跳，甚至有忠实粉丝发出感叹：</span></span><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">“除非这颗‘牛油果’能惊世骇俗，否则属于扎克伯格的时代，可能真的要结束了。”</span></span></b></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppk5e\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851486\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=068d1b16&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHp8QJSvdPzF1icMb5w3x1Umm9iblCmmT5TicezNBeKzhc5teZXS1PElhxw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp1ega\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdk0j\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizbuc8316ub\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">AI战略“急刹车”：</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppoad\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdkv8\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizbuc8316ub\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">从Llama开源到Avocado闭源</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppqbj\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdvzb\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">Meta的AI路线图正经历一场“一百八十度大转弯”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp6x9\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd1xnd\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">过去，Llama系列以其开源特性独树一帜，旨在依靠社区力量快速缩小与闭源模型的差距。但现实是，开源的风险逐渐浮现，不仅Llama 4的发布未达预期，未能有效吸引开发者，更有竞争对手甚至中国AI实验室利用其架构，这无疑给Meta敲响了警钟。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9ppo6q\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048224\" data-ratio=\"0.5257575757575758\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"660\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=71cbb966&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxk7T4wvnnvicb5kmFdvibmynma0U17wPt4NaykmicH6JiacAZJ2rYAhrqDg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pplqa\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdqcp\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizcbabgaw6\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">（图片由AI生成）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp1hf\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdzo2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">知情人士透露，Meta将于2026年第一季度发布的Llama继任者，极有可能是一款专有（闭源）模型。</span></span></b><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">&nbsp;这意味着外部开发者将无法再自由获取其核心“权重”和组件。这种从开放到封闭的巨大转变，标志着Meta正“收紧控制，重塑创新策略”，以更好地保护知识产权，并实现直接盈利。</span></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp18ns\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd14v\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">部分网友认为，这是“明智的转型”，尤其是在Reality Labs近期削减成本之后，市场似乎更青睐专注于实体AI产品而非元宇宙。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pp23bk\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048225\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4099173553719009\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"605\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=602c8410&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxWX5eAYFQia7mhyfx1Ojq3535esgs7GZRLicTY1SIJBYnpVuej6cqRQBg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq35e\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"503048226\" data-ratio=\"1.1959798994974875\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"597\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=13620287&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxib2icckeRpX8GCvdFTKhuLt9Vtk3JPjbDyzQNYW6nrqsFREeSHQMibLZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqit5\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hdviu\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">但也有人质疑，除非牛油果能做到“惊世骇俗”，否则扎克伯格的时代可能真要“结束了”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1gys\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048239\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.27638190954773867\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"597\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43388806&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxhpFZobr2sDk3pu78KFwibj1ibBib2hUE52kH0ZptGg78Y4lribYRNe2caA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1ln4\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hd60b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">也有网友犀利指出，Meta的现状可谓“财力雄厚，方向迷离”。公司在多个前沿领域广泛布局，却似乎始终缺乏一个聚焦的战略核心，颇有些“弹药充足，却不知该瞄准何方”的意味。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1v8a\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048246\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5468227424749164\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"598\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1a847655&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxXFLOkicrR2w7JyaysibNkR0Vm5mEFyD6JQrXpQ4Ozn1jJYvPRKS8A4VA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-acti