s GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he19gt\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">在外部竞争对手——谷歌发布Gemini 3、OpenAI宣布GPT-5更新、Anthropic推出Claude Opus 4.5——的“组合拳”攻势下，内部的压力也水涨船高。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1lqa\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048249\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5409090909090909\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"660\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5caf552e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxs84fVzFDHNLWHyx1wjqgshskyr2ziaib9IvSZQ9XmwECfsrMKdMOr6jw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;text-align: center;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq6yl\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:12px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he1oes\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizccvkg1mpa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(127, 127, 127);\">（图片由AI生成）</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1a3m\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hea2b\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">知情人士称，超级智能团队内部普遍感到压力山大，每周工作70小时已成常态。汪滔和弗里德曼面临着交付一款顶级AI模型的“巨大压力”。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqwot\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he6j2\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">弗里德曼负责的AI生成短视频流Vibes，因被广泛视为逊于OpenAI的Sora 2，且缺乏逼真的口型同步等关键功能而遭受质疑，这进一步凸显了Meta在消费级AI产品上的“落后身位”。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqev\"><img data-imgfileid=\"502851488\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.15204678362573099\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"684\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e3903754&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FrwnawOsSCFp4iatBAbsJzvVraDq6Xh5OHbibjrtOUPcIJ97eDllknPibqJcjaTO0xclRf0UKBH8hLvEwbOEwtxiaAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1b7j\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he1jjj\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizc410k1231\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">结语：</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq64g\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he6u0\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-size:20px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizc410k1231\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">牛油果，Meta AI的最后一搏？</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqwlf\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he1e3l\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">从对Llama的高度乐观到对牛油果的战略加码，Meta的AI战略经历了一次痛苦的洗牌。放弃纯粹的开源模式，转向更具竞争力的闭源路线，体现了该公司在面对OpenAI等对手时的务实与焦急。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1nv1\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he19w2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">正如另一条评论所调侃的，扎克伯格似乎在AI领域复刻了元宇宙的剧本。昔日重金投入VR赛道却回声寥寥，如今又向“牛油果”项目注入巨资奋力追赶。然而环顾四周，竞争对手早已绝尘而去，留给Meta的挑战愈发严峻。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqzq0\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048250\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7533333333333333\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"600\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0a05de4e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxB7jIhncJnwLicIvjo8miarxcocaHvn1icASn1jabVyvbricLa3P2zVXHFw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left:1em;font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.75em;font-style:normal;margin-bottom:0px;margin-right:1em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1abz\"><img data-imgfileid=\"503048251\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.1440397350993377\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"604\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit;border: 0px;max-width: 100%;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=43a44247&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FrwnawOsSCFqDyYwaianMI9uXgG63CMsIxEXvUOX3MuYkpDbJLvnFxBiaibibcQo2scc3dJglHxRnbbJmjRTLjBJRZw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqs4d\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:1px;font-size:15px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\" mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0hexv1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(89, 89, 89);\">Meta的这场AI豪赌，赌注之大令人咋舌：百亿美元的资金、颠覆性的文化重塑，以及整个公司的未来航向。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pqnmk\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he117q\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">然而，高投入未必能换来高回报。正如网友所担忧的那样，如果“牛油果”重蹈元宇宙的覆辙，那么Meta将面临的不仅仅是股价的波动，而是被时代抛弃的风险。</span></span></b></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 1em;margin-right: 1em;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mizdd9pq1wr9\"><b mpa-font-style=\"mizdd0he8y\" style=\"font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 1px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:bold;\">这一次，扎克伯格输不起。</span></span></b></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章深度剖析了 Meta 在 AI 战略上的重大转变，从开源 Llama 转向闭源模型“Avocado”，揭示了其背后的人才、资金投入、内部文化冲突以及在商业上豪赌 AI 的挑战与风险。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章深度剖析了 Meta 在 AI 战略上的重大转变，从开源 Llama 转向闭源模型“Avocado”，揭示了其背后的人才、资金投入、内部文化冲突以及在商业上豪赌 AI 的挑战与风险。",
  "summary": "文章详细探讨了 Meta AI 战略从 Llama 的开源转向代号为“Avocado”的闭源研究的深层原因及影响。Meta 在面对外部竞争加剧和 Llama 开源未达预期目标的情况下，调整了战略重心，计划于明年一季度发布闭源模型，旨在更好地保护知识产权并实现盈利。为实现这一转型，Meta 不仅斥资 143 亿美元引进 AI 顶尖人才，大幅提高 AI 投资预算，还在内部进行了大刀阔斧的重组和裁员，引发了文化冲突和巨大的交付压力。文章指出，尽管 Meta 广告业务表现强劲，但高额投入和战略反复令华尔街充满疑虑，并认为“Avocado”的成败将直接决定 Meta 在 AI 时代的未来。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
